file.name: api.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
paths:
components:
  schemas:
    ContainsArrayOfArrays:
      type: object
      properties:
        array_of_arrays:
          type: array
          items:
            $ref: "#/components/schemas/ArrayOfSomething"

    ArrayOfSomething:
      type: array
      items:
        $ref: "#/components/schemas/Something"

    Something:
      type: object
      required:
        grams
      properties:
        some_value:
          type: integer
          example: 100
          
    ArraySimpleInLined:
      type: object
      required:
        - quantities
      properties:
        quantities:
          type: array
          items:
            type: integer
            format: int64

    ContainsArrayRef:
      type: object
      required:
        - weight_on_mars
      properties:
        weight_on_mars:
          type: array
          items:
            $ref: "#/components/schemas/ArrayRef"
    ArrayRef:
      type: object
      required:
        grams
      properties:
        grams:
          type: integer
          example: 100

Error:
unmarshal: yaml: unmarshal errors:
  yaml: line 1: cannot unmarshal !!str `grams` into []string; yaml: line 1: cannot unmarshal !!str `grams` into []string
